{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.1","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:1","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Adresse et salutation<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-2: cf. 2 Pi 1:1, 2. Ja 1:1. Jud 1, 2.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Pierre, ap\u00f4tre de J\u00e9sus-Christ, \u00e0 ceux qui sont \u00e9trangers et dispers\u00e9s dans le Pont, la Galatie, la Cappadoce, l\u2019Asie et la Bithynie,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.2","name":"1 Pierre 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.20","name":"Jacques 5:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.2","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:2","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>et qui sont \u00e9lus selon la prescience de Dieu le P\u00e8re, par la sanctification de l\u2019Esprit, afin qu\u2019ils deviennent ob\u00e9issants, et qu\u2019ils participent \u00e0 l\u2019aspersion du sang de J\u00e9sus-Christ: que la gr\u00e2ce et la paix vous soient multipli\u00e9es!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.3","name":"1 Pierre 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.1","name":"1 Pierre 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.3","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:3","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.004,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Actions de gr\u00e2ces au sujet de l\u2019esp\u00e9rance du salut<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 3-12: cf. (\u00c9p 2:4-8. 1 Co 15:20-23. Col 1:5, 12, 13.) (Ro 8:17, 18. 2 Co 4:17, 18. 1 Jn 3:1, 2.) (Mt 13:17. Ro 16:25, 26.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>\n    B\u00e9ni soit Dieu, le P\u00e8re de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ, qui, selon sa grande mis\u00e9ricorde, nous a r\u00e9g\u00e9n\u00e9r\u00e9s, pour une esp\u00e9rance vivante, par la r\u00e9surrection de J\u00e9sus-Christ d\u2019entre les morts,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.4","name":"1 Pierre 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.2","name":"1 Pierre 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.4","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:4","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>pour un h\u00e9ritage qui ne se peut ni corrompre, ni souiller, ni fl\u00e9trir, lequel vous est r\u00e9serv\u00e9 dans les cieux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.5","name":"1 Pierre 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.3","name":"1 Pierre 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.5","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:5","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>\u00e0 vous qui, par la puissance de Dieu, \u00eates gard\u00e9s par la foi pour le salut pr\u00eat \u00e0 \u00eatre r\u00e9v\u00e9l\u00e9 dans les derniers temps!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.6","name":"1 Pierre 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.4","name":"1 Pierre 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.6","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:6","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>C\u2019est l\u00e0 ce qui fait votre joie, quoique maintenant, puisqu\u2019il le faut, vous soyez attrist\u00e9s pour un peu de temps par diverses \u00e9preuves,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.7","name":"1 Pierre 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.5","name":"1 Pierre 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.7","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:7","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>afin que l\u2019\u00e9preuve de votre foi, plus pr\u00e9cieuse que l\u2019or p\u00e9rissable (qui cependant est \u00e9prouv\u00e9 par le feu), ait pour r\u00e9sultat la louange, la gloire et l\u2019honneur, lorsque J\u00e9sus-Christ appara\u00eetra,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.8","name":"1 Pierre 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.6","name":"1 Pierre 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.8","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:8","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>lui que vous aimez sans l\u2019avoir vu, en qui vous croyez sans le voir encore, vous r\u00e9jouissant d\u2019une joie ineffable et glorieuse,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.9","name":"1 Pierre 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.7","name":"1 Pierre 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.9","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:9","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>parce que vous obtiendrez le salut de vos \u00e2mes pour prix de votre foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.10","name":"1 Pierre 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.8","name":"1 Pierre 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.10","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:10","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Les proph\u00e8tes, qui ont proph\u00e9tis\u00e9 touchant la gr\u00e2ce qui vous \u00e9tait r\u00e9serv\u00e9e, ont fait de ce salut l\u2019objet de leurs recherches et de leurs investigations,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.11","name":"1 Pierre 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.9","name":"1 Pierre 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.11","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:11","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>voulant sonder l\u2019\u00e9poque et les circonstances marqu\u00e9es par l\u2019Esprit de Christ qui \u00e9tait en eux, et qui attestait d\u2019avance les souffrances de Christ et la gloire dont elles seraient suivies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.12","name":"1 Pierre 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.10","name":"1 Pierre 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.12","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:12","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Il leur fut r\u00e9v\u00e9l\u00e9 que ce n\u2019\u00e9tait pas pour eux-m\u00eames, mais pour vous, qu\u2019ils \u00e9taient les dispensateurs de ces choses, que vous ont annonc\u00e9es maintenant ceux qui vous ont pr\u00each\u00e9 l\u2019\u00c9vangile par le Saint-Esprit envoy\u00e9 du ciel, et dans lesquelles les anges d\u00e9sirent plonger leurs regards.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.13","name":"1 Pierre 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.11","name":"1 Pierre 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.13","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:13","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortation \u00e0 la saintet\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-25: cf. (1 Th 5:8, 9. \u00c9p 5:1. H\u00e9 12:14.) (1 Co 6:20. Tit 2:11-14.) (1 Jn 5:1. Ja 1:18.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>\n    C\u2019est pourquoi, ceignez les reins de votre entendement, soyez sobres, et ayez une enti\u00e8re esp\u00e9rance dans la gr\u00e2ce qui vous sera apport\u00e9e, lorsque J\u00e9sus-Christ appara\u00eetra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.14","name":"1 Pierre 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.12","name":"1 Pierre 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.14","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:14","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Comme des enfants ob\u00e9issants, ne vous conformez pas aux convoitises que vous aviez autrefois, quand vous \u00e9tiez dans l\u2019ignorance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.15","name":"1 Pierre 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.13","name":"1 Pierre 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.15","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:15","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Mais, puisque celui qui vous a appel\u00e9s est saint, vous aussi soyez saints dans toute votre conduite,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.16","name":"1 Pierre 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.14","name":"1 Pierre 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.16","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:16","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>selon qu\u2019il est \u00e9crit: Vous serez saints, car je suis saint.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.17","name":"1 Pierre 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.15","name":"1 Pierre 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.17","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:17","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et si vous invoquez comme P\u00e8re celui qui juge selon l\u2019\u0153uvre de chacun, sans acception de personnes, conduisez-vous avec crainte pendant le temps de votre p\u00e8lerinage,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.18","name":"1 Pierre 1:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.16","name":"1 Pierre 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.18","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:18","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>sachant que ce n\u2019est pas par des choses p\u00e9rissables, par de l\u2019argent ou de l\u2019or, que vous avez \u00e9t\u00e9 rachet\u00e9s de la vaine mani\u00e8re de vivre que vous aviez h\u00e9rit\u00e9e de vos p\u00e8res,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.19","name":"1 Pierre 1:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.17","name":"1 Pierre 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.19","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:19","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>mais par le sang pr\u00e9cieux de Christ, comme d\u2019un agneau sans d\u00e9faut et sans tache,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.20","name":"1 Pierre 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.18","name":"1 Pierre 1:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.20","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:20","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>pr\u00e9destin\u00e9 avant la fondation du monde, et manifest\u00e9 \u00e0 la fin des temps, \u00e0 cause de vous,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.21","name":"1 Pierre 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.19","name":"1 Pierre 1:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.21","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:21","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>qui par lui croyez en Dieu, lequel l\u2019a ressuscit\u00e9 des morts et lui a donn\u00e9 la gloire, en sorte que votre foi et votre esp\u00e9rance reposent sur Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.22","name":"1 Pierre 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.20","name":"1 Pierre 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.22","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:22","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Ayant purifi\u00e9 vos \u00e2mes en ob\u00e9issant \u00e0 la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 pour avoir un amour fraternel sinc\u00e8re, aimez-vous ardemment les uns les autres, de tout votre c\u0153ur,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.23","name":"1 Pierre 1:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.21","name":"1 Pierre 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.23","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:23","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>puisque vous avez \u00e9t\u00e9 r\u00e9g\u00e9n\u00e9r\u00e9s, non par une semence corruptible, mais par une semence incorruptible, par la parole vivante et permanente de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.24","name":"1 Pierre 1:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.22","name":"1 Pierre 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.24","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:24","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Car<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Toute chair est comme l\u2019herbe,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">et toute sa gloire comme la fleur de l\u2019herbe.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u2019herbe s\u00e8che, et la fleur tombe;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.25","name":"1 Pierre 1:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.23","name":"1 Pierre 1:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.25","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 1:25","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Pet.1.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>mais la parole du Seigneur demeure \u00e9ternellement.<\/p>\n<p class=\"m\">Et cette parole est celle qui vous a \u00e9t\u00e9 annonc\u00e9e par l\u2019\u00c9vangile.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1","name":"1 Pierre 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.1","name":"1 Pierre 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.24","name":"1 Pierre 1:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb6c05499.77788207');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6c05499.77788207\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb6c05499.77788207","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb6c05499.77788207'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6c05499.77788207\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}